OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1773144737
OL,3,CMan arrested after crash which injured
OL,4,Cwoman and four children
OL,6,FThe 53-year-old woman and one of the
OL,7,Fchildren were treated for serious
OL,8,Finjuries that are not thought to be
OL,9,Flife changing, additionally two other
OL,10,Fchildren who were in the vehicle were
OL,11,Ftreated for their injuries upon
OL,12,Fattendance to hospital.
OL,14,FA 44-year-old man, the driver of the
OL,15,FBMW, has been arrested on suspicion of
OL,16,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,17,Fdriving, driving whilst above the
OL,18,Flegal alcohol limit and failing to
OL,19,Fprovide a specimen for analysis.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/3
